  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Valedictus is a Detroit Consolidated design that came out of the 32nd century MAF procurement pipeline, built at a time when the Magistracy was watching the Wolf Empire consolidate power and needed assault-weight hardware that could handle a broad range of battlefield problems rather than excel at just one thing. The Bombast Laser never found wide adoption because it demands more from a pilot than most weapons do, but Detroit Consolidated bet on Canopian MechWarriors being good enough to use it properly. From what the Ebon Magistrate did with it in Marian Hegemony raids, that bet paid off.",
